---
title: Southern Seafood Cookout with Lemon Garlic Butter
description: Ring in the weekend with one of the ultimate backyard party meals! Paying homage to the classic Louisiana seafood boil, we've taken those same great flavours and made it grill friendly for that delicious smoky flavour we all know and love. Bibs are definitely recommended!
